themas.title: General de Gaulle's Visit to Cambodia (1966)
themas.description: On September 1st, 1966 at 9h35, in front of 200.000 people, General De Gaulle gave a speech of extreme solemnity in Phnom Penh, in a large stadium newly inaugurated by Prince Sihanouk. His speech marked the important eve...
